<A HREF="http://sr.amiga.tm/" TARGET="_new"><IMG ALT="Silent Redemption Member" BORDER=0 SRC="http://home1.gte.net/res007bh/Thoricwarlordsig_copy.gif"></A> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uzakumara.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zakumara</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 44<br> <font color=#CC9900>(5/11/01 3:58:20 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Lord Ghiosk in CoM</span><hr size=1> I know CoM a bit, when you mean acrros bridge, you mean the bridge where you go when you do &quot;loop&quot; ? There is a bridge in front of door (not sure if it is the locked door or not) with 2 platforms above water where ther is several ghost/undead spawn ? is it the best place to pull reaver ? because it is a bit tight and if mob falls in water might be a dodgy issue with pathing. <p>Zak<br>
